page.title: 08My Eleventh Birthday
page.content: I woke up on Monday morning at 4 25am. It was light outside and my quilt had fallen off my bed. I pulled it back on and there lying on the floor were three{presents.}"Great" I thought and a card extra big. I decided I should leave it till the proper morning about 8 00am. But some how I could'nt. I went into my mum's bedroom and I took my{presents}with me. I put them down on the bed and woke my mum up. She said I could open them in my room so I went to my room and opened them. There were some sandals and a{little pony purse. My {best present}came five days later a Raleigh{bike}mauve with three gears.
